        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mb-10 sm:mb-12">
          <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary btn-md sm:btn-lg hero-cta">無料で始める</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-sm text-base-content/60 hero-label">配信先:<span class="text-xs ml-2">（順次追加予定）</span></span>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:flex sm:flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-4 sm:gap-6">
            <img src="/badges/spotify.svg" alt="Listen on Spotify" class="h-8 sm:h-10 mx-auto hero-badge hero-badge-1" />
            <img src="/badges/apple-podcasts.svg" alt="Listen on Apple Podcasts" class="h-8 sm:h-10 mx-auto hero-badge hero-badge-2" />
            <img src="/badges/amazon-music.svg" alt="Listen on Amazon Music" class="h-8 sm:h-10 mx-auto hero-badge hero-badge-3" />
