            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:flex sm:flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-3 sm:gap-6 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
              <img src="/badges/spotify.svg" alt="Spotify" class="h-8 sm:h-10 mx-auto animate-platform" data-delay="600" />
              <img src="/badges/apple-podcasts.svg" alt="Apple Podcasts" class="h-8 sm:h-10 mx-auto animate-platform" data-delay="750" />
              <img src="/badges/amazon-music.svg" alt="Amazon Music" class="h-8 sm:h-10 mx-auto animate-platform" data-delay="900" />
              <img src="/badges/youtube-music.svg" alt="YouTube Music" class="h-8 sm:h-10 mx-auto animate-platform" data-delay="1050" />
            </div>
            <p class="text-center text-sm sm:text-base text-base-content/70 animate-fade-up" data-delay="1200">それぞれに登録して、<br class="sm:hidden" />それぞれの管理画面で確認して...</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Solution -->
        <div class="bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl p-5 sm:p-8 text-center animate-slide-up" data-delay="1400">
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-5 sm:mb-6">
            PODDOCKなら、<br class="sm:hidden" />ひとつの画面ですべて管理。
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-3 sm:gap-8 mb-5 sm:mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 animate-step" data-delay="1700">
              <span class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-content flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm sm:text-base">1</span>
              <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">番組を作る</span>
            </div>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-base-content/30 hidden sm:block animate-step" data-delay="1850" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
